<script id="loading" type="text/template">
        data:image/jpg;base64,
    </script>

const mainDiv = document.getElementById("main");
        const loading = document.getElementById("loading").innerText;
        const loadImages = function () {
            var images = document.getElementsByTagName("img");
            for (let idx = 0; idx < images.length; idx++) {
                var id = images[idx].getAttribute("data-src");                
                var request = `{
    targets(where: {
      id: {
        eq: "${id}"
      }
    }) {
         thumbnail
    }
}`;
                (function (request, img) {


                    fetch("https://localhost:{port}/graphql", {
                        method: "POST",
                        body: JSON.stringify({
                            query: request
                        }),
                        headers: {
                            "Content-Type": "application/json"
                        }
                    })
                        .then(function (result) {
                            result.json().then(function (json) {
                                img.src = json.data.targets[0].thumbnail;
                                console.log(img.src);
                            })
                        });
                })(request, images[idx]);
            }
        };
                
        const show = function (resp) {
            list = resp.data.targets;
            mainDiv.innerHTML = "";
            for (var idx = 0; idx < list.length; idx++) {
                const target = list[idx];
                const newDiv = document.createElement("div");
                newDiv.classList.add("card");
                newDiv.innerHTML = `<b>M${target.index}</b><br/>` +
                    `<img data-src="${target.id}" src="${loading}"/><br/>` +
                    `<p>${target.nGCDesignation}</p>`;
                mainDiv.appendChild(newDiv);
            }
            loadImages();
        };
        setTimeout(function () {
            fetch("https://localhost:{port}/graphql", {
                method: "POST",
                body: JSON.stringify({
                    query: `{
    targets(where: {
      thumbnail: {
        nstartsWith: "data:image/jpg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQEA8ADwAAD/2wBDAAIBAQIBAQICAgICAgICAwUDAwMDAw"
      }
    }, order: {
      index: ASC
    }) {
         index,
         id,
         nGCDesignation
    }
}`}),
                headers: {
                    "Content-Type": "application/json"
                }
            })
                .then(function (result) {
                    result.json().then(function (json) {
                        show(json);
                    })
                });
        }, 0);
